{
  "stem": "19596.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that particular time, I was just studying the basics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what I wanted to really do is go to aeronautic engineering.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we have been suffering a bit-- started to suffer as a Jew in that school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I tried to be, because the teacher said always, about Ginsberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're so clever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're supposed to be so clever a race.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell me the answer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the whole class was laughing, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had to get up and give him the answer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then outside, next to me were-- I was sitting with Hitler Youth brownshirts, the shorts and little daggers, going to school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what I had to put up with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that particular time, we were-- we were actually starting to get restricted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1937.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jew--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father used to go out on the main street in Kurfuerstendamm, which was one of the biggest streets in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And business was done in coffeehouses, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In huge, big coffeehouses with-- with-- with cake and-- and-- and coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the real estate agents used to come to one big-- big coffeehouse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to do business there, selling and buying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another coffeehouse was restricted for other traits, and professions, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he used to go out every day into town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother was home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then in the evening, sometime they went out in the theater, or live show, or concert.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was very musical.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was-- she was studying in the conservatorium in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went to the conservatorium in Kiev when she was 17, 18 years of age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because the Russian Revolution started in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and then they were still young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got out in 1922--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--after Russian Revolution.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
